{"tid":316453,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞接力] 「信下去 便確定我共你 能傳心 能連起」","createTime":"2017-07-10T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T19:36:51.000Z","uid":40429,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"836d11124da43dd7261c34e3e92abae920e5cea8","tid":316453,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"「信下去　便確定我共你　能傳心　能連起」<br />\n咪亂信　但你地咪話我　葡提子　心理<br />\n<br />\n我們　將所見跟所聞<br />\n一針見血新聞　都宣泄不甘<br />\n<br />\n個個將你吹奏　明明其實荒謬<br />\n就用你把金口　線上廢up　吹幾句　不深究<br />\n尋覓龜頭　憑師傅那量子夠<br />\n沒料那幅相後 塑化龜已無愁沒憂<br />\n啞口無言　柒到呢　望你樣　很足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾人人亦嫌棄　最尾人人亦凌欺<br />\n外面通通睇你死　有線新聞跣柒你<br />\n勝過絕美的晨曦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊接力恥笑喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f5bcddcb8222beacfa07cb16d5ed6010326403","tid":316453,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:46:40.000Z","msg":"接力接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7d6cf9d742e7ef7ae37c790027d5e59e000d1e","tid":316453,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"接力接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60e86830c2bdb7e73f4015186707ec3ea355c82","tid":316453,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"睇到塑化龜先知講緊動物傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb76605fb3b05ac752b8b10479a09eb1a479d4c","tid":316453,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到塑化龜先知講緊動物傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3193e7c903aaa4b3a4873f530f89362b93130742","tid":3